{"tid":1779184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鬼拍後尾枕 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-11T13:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T13:48:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29368fb3b7ca1212a5c1fa415175cac504c95560","tid":1779184,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191211/20822709/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191211%2F20822709%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnALtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=4a7d1ef0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191211%2F20822709%2F&h=fcf2eda0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191211/20822709/</a><br />\n<br />\n鬼拍後尾枕 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191211/large/1575970789_f071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191211%2Flarge%2F1575970789_f071.jpg&h=e5ef562b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNOW新聞截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，黑警喬裝黑衣人示威者，縱火、扔汽油彈、挑釁生事惹起激烈行動&hellip;&hellip;這不是秘密也無法隱瞞，現今科技發達，且人人都可當記者，現場拍攝揭穿勾當。<br />\n<br />\n插贓嫁禍或誣陷的惡行，不知如何被常規化、合理化，隻手遮天。像128國際人權日大遊行，百萬人都沿途逼爆，金鐘高等法院及終審法院，傍晚被黑衣人扔擲汽油彈及雜物起火。有人拍到兩人行動（標準身材黑影），天橋處同伴把風都有亮燈暗號。政府、律政司、警方政客、奴才紛紛指責暴徒──但法院是社會守護對象，早前禁蒙面法違憲司法覆核勝訴，亦有些法官秉公辦理斥律政司濫捕濫告，看不到攻擊法院之原因。當然，要依法調查檢控──但一直以來警方都抓不到（或一聲「自己人」抓了也放）。<br />\n<br />\n有人send來「警謊」公告，發言人「義正辭嚴」道：「希望市民千祈唔好掉以輕心，以為我哋打爛嘅──係『暴徒』打爛嘅，只係一啲冇靈魂嘅死物，而忘記咗&hellip;&hellip;」真是鬼拍後尾枕！各方瘋傳要睇快啲睇，可能好快冇咗，所以立此存照。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「鬼」，未必是命案冤魂，而是「心中有鬼」，亦良知、是非之心、潛意識的贖罪真言。大人大姐，好人好姐，淪為黑警，政治棋子、幫兇，天天說謊，良心過意不去。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"3072aa86f72d60dc3249a9320b318256df9f18b3","tid":1779184,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"【和你Read】【國際陣線】聯合國批監警會無實權，促港府成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"207a124f1d94020d98ca9615286674af202fa800","tid":1779184,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"其實今日香港都拎到美國同加拿大關注<br />\n可唔可以幫拖<span style=\"color: gold;\">rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<br />\n【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}